That new woman! The one I have been, for some reason, reporting on, she is 
leaving town. She has bought a Razor Scooter from the pawn shop, and is using 
it to skim her way down the shoulder of Route 800. Destination, and origin, 
both unknown. But we know where she is now. Good for us!
